The Nexgen Dehumidifier helps in reducing the humidity level in a room. The I-Detect Technology enables the AC to shut down in case of any errors which is then displayed as per code. product_description: Bask in the cool glory of the Voltas 123V CAZR Split Inverter AC, engineered for your utmost relaxation. The innovative air conditioner comes with a steady cooling compressor and smart dehumidifier. This split inverter air conditioner boasts a simplistic yet appealing design and packs in impressive features that will wow you over. With 1.0 tonnage capacity, this AC is ideal for small rooms. The Voltas split air conditioner operates across a wide range of voltages to embrace you and your loved ones in the chilly breeze despite voltage fluctuations. Efficient Cooling At All Times The Voltas 123V CAZR Split Inverter AC packs in a steady cooling compressor for efficient cooling at all times. It reduces power consumption by maintaining an ideal temperature without frequently turning the compressor on and off. Besides, its stabilizer free operation ensures super smooth functioning under wide voltage fluctuations from 150V - 270V, without the need of a stabilizer. Durable Copper Coil Condenser The amazing copper condenser coil of this Voltas 123V CAZR Split Inverter AC has been tested for durability and works wonders. The copper coil helps transfer heat faster than aluminium coils and are also sturdier. Its high heat transfer ability aims to cool the room faster in the process. Sleep Mode for Cosy Napping Sessions The Voltas 123V CAZR Split Inverter AC comes with an anti-dust filter for providing you with clean air. The anti-dust filter keeps the dust out of the room so that you can breathe in the fresh air. This air conditioner also employs a Smart Diagnosis mode so that troubles are determined even before they occur. In addition to that, it comes with a Sleep Mode which adjusts the temperature accordingly so that you can nap in peace.
